OL,3,CMan, 82, who befriended families to
OL,4,Csexually abuse children jailed
OL,6,FA man from Guernsey has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor a series of serious historic sex
OL,8,Foffences against two children, one
OL,9,Ffrom the age of seven.
OL,11,FMichael Derek Cotterill, 82, was
OL,12,Fsentenced at the island's Royal Court
OL,13,Fto eight years and ten months in
OL,14,Fprison for his actions in the 1980s.
