OL,3,CMan, 82, who befriended families to
OL,4,Csexually abuse children jailed
OL,6,FIt follows a week-long trial in
OL,7,FJanuary where Cotterill was found
OL,8,Fguilty of two counts of indecent
OL,9,Fassault, five counts of inciting a
OL,10,Fchild to commit an act of gross
OL,11,Findecency, and one count of common
OL,12,Fassault on a child.
OL,14,FAn investigation opened into Cotterill
OL,15,Fin June 2022 when Guernsey Police
OL,16,Freceived a report from a woman in her
OL,17,F40s claiming she had been sexually
OL,18,Fabused by him between the ages of
OL,19,Fseven and nine.
