OL,3,CMan, 82, who befriended families to
OL,4,Csexually abuse children jailed
OL,6,FA second woman came forward while
OL,7,Fthese allegations were being looked
OL,8,Finto, saying she had also been
OL,9,Fsexually abused by Cotterill when she
OL,10,Fwas 12 - the two women did not know
OL,11,Feach other.
OL,13,FThe court found that Cotterill
OL,14,Fdeliberately befriended the families
OL,15,Fof the children he was abusing to gain
OL,16,Feasy access to them.
