OL,3,CMan, 82, who befriended families to
OL,4,Csexually abuse children jailed
OL,6,FSpeaking about the case, Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Julie Palmer said: "No
OL,8,Fchild should ever be subjected to this
OL,9,Fhorrific abuse or have their innocence
OL,10,Ftaken away from them in this way.
OL,12,F"I hope these convictions serve as an
OL,13,Fimportant message to people who have
OL,14,Fbeen victims of crimes such as these:
OL,15,Fif they come forward, regardless of
OL,16,Fwhen the offence occurred, we will
OL,17,Frelentlessly pursue offenders and do
OL,18,Four best to bring justice for victims.
