OL,6,F"If you or someone you know has been
OL,7,Fthe victim of any form of sexual
OL,8,Fabuse, please report it to the
OL,9,FGuernsey Police at any time, no matter
OL,10,Fhow long after the events."
OL,12,FThe force also thanked both women for
OL,13,Ftheir bravery in coming forward and
OL,14,Fgiving evidence in court after a
OL,15,Flengthy investigation.
